<pre>
Date: Wed, 05 Nov 1997 16:59:34 -0800
From: Rick Jones &lt;<a href="mailto:raj@cup.hp.com">raj@cup.hp.com</a>&gt;
Reply-To: <a href="mailto:raj@cup.hp.com">raj@cup.hp.com</a>
